bụ klọb bọọlụ nke dị n'afọ Lagos

N'afọ 2015/2016, Ikorodu United gbara bọọlụ na Nigeria Premier League mgbe ọ nwetasịrị nkwalite n'usoro site na Nigeria Nationwide League na Nigeria National League.
Ikorodu United FC bụ ndị Abia Warriors FC jidere na 1-1 draw na egwuregwu mbụ ha na Nigerian Professional Football league na akụkọ ihe mere eme nke klọb ahụ n'ụbọchị egwuregwu mbụ n'ala ụlọ Onikan Stadium, nwere ike ịba mmadụ puku iri Lagos Steeti.
Onikan Stadium nke nwere ike ịba mmadụ puku ise bụ ebe obibi nke Ikorodu United F.C.
